				<li class="ListParagraph" style="margin-top:2.05pt; margin-right:5.8pt; line-height:115%; font-size:12pt; list-style-position:inside">
					<span style="width:3.73pt; font:7pt 'Times New Roman'; display:inline-block">&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="line-height:115%; font-size:11pt">Pelo CONTRATANTE mediante solicitação de cancelamento, apresentada com 30 dias</span><span style="line-height:115%; font-size:11pt; letter-spacing:-0.35pt"> </span><span style="line-height:115%; font-size:11pt">de antecedência, enviada para os contatos a seguir estabelecidos neste Contrato;</span>
					<ol class="awlist2" style="margin-right:0pt; margin-left:0pt; padding-left:0pt">
						<li class="ListParagraph" style="margin-right:5.5pt; margin-left:0pt; font-size:12pt">
							<span style="width:3.73pt; font:7pt 'Times New Roman'; display:inline-block">&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="line-height:115%; font-size:11pt">Se o CONTRATANTE requerer a rescisão do Contrato</span><span style="line-height:115%; font-size:11pt; letter-spacing:-0.3pt"> </span><span style="line-height:115%; font-size:11pt">no</span><span style="line-height:115%; font-size:11pt; letter-spacing:-0.3pt"> </span><span style="line-height:115%; font-size:11pt">mesmo</span><span style="line-height:115%; font-size:11pt; letter-spacing:-0.3pt"> </span><span style="line-height:115%; font-size:11pt">ano</span><span style="line-height:115%; font-size:11pt; letter-spacing:-0.3pt"> </span><span style="line-height:115%; font-size:11pt">da</span><span style="line-height:115%; font-size:11pt; letter-spacing:-0.3pt"> </span><span style="line-height:115%; font-size:11pt">filiação.</span>
