					<span style="width:2.95pt; font:7pt 'Times New Roman'; display:inline-block">&#xa0; </span><span style="font-size:11pt; letter-spacing:-0.1pt">Pela</span><span style="font-size:11pt; letter-spacing:0.05pt"> </span><span style="font-size:11pt; letter-spacing:-0.1pt">CONTRATADA</span><span style="font-size:11pt; letter-spacing:-0.65pt"> </span><span style="font-size:11pt; letter-spacing:-0.1pt">nos</span><span style="font-size:11pt; letter-spacing:0.05pt"> </span><span style="font-size:11pt; letter-spacing:-0.1pt">seguintes</span><span style="font-size:11pt; letter-spacing:0.1pt"> </span><span style="font-size:11pt; letter-spacing:-0.1pt">casos:</span>
					<ol class="awlist2" style="margin-right:0pt; margin-left:0pt; padding-left:0pt">
						<li class="ListParagraph" style="margin-top:2.1pt; margin-right:5.85pt; margin-left:-12.95pt; line-height:115%; font-size:12pt; list-style-position:inside">
							<span style="width:5.95pt; font:7pt 'Times New Roman'; display:inline-block">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="line-height:115%; font-size:11pt">mediante comunicação formal com 30 (trinta) dias de antecedência, enviada para os contatos a seguir estabelecidos neste Contrato e estando com todas as mensalidades em dia.</span>
