						<li class="ListParagraph" style="margin-right:5.35pt; margin-left:-12.95pt; line-height:115%; font-size:12pt; list-style-position:inside">
							<span style="width:2.95pt; font:7pt 'Times New Roman'; display:inline-block">&#xa0; </span><span style="line-height:115%; font-size:11pt">de</span><span style="line-height:115%; font-size:11pt; letter-spacing:-0.2pt"> </span><span style="line-height:115%; font-size:11pt">forma</span><span style="line-height:115%; font-size:11pt; letter-spacing:-0.2pt"> </span><span style="line-height:115%; font-size:11pt">automática</span><span style="line-height:115%; font-size:11pt; letter-spacing:-0.2pt"> </span><span style="line-height:115%; font-size:11pt">no</span><span style="line-height:115%; font-size:11pt; letter-spacing:-0.2pt"> </span><span style="line-height:115%; font-size:11pt">caso</span><span style="line-height:115%; font-size:11pt; letter-spacing:-0.2pt"> </span><span style="line-height:115%; font-size:11pt">de</span><span style="line-height:115%; font-size:11pt; letter-spacing:-0.2pt"> </span><span style="line-height:115%; font-size:11pt">justa</span><span style="line-height:115%; font-size:11pt; letter-spacing:-0.2pt"> </span><span style="line-height:115%; font-size:11pt">causa,</span><span style="line-height:115%; font-size:11pt; letter-spacing:-0.2pt"> </span><span style="line-height:115%; font-size:11pt">decorrente</span><span style="line-height:115%; font-size:11pt; letter-spacing:-0.2pt"> </span><span style="line-height:115%; font-size:11pt">de:</span><span style="line-height:115%; font-size:11pt; letter-spacing:-0.2pt"> </span><span style="line-height:115%; font-size:11pt">1)</span><span style="line-height:115%; font-size:11pt; letter-spacing:-0.2pt"> </span><span style="line-height:115%; font-size:11pt">comportamento</span><span style="line-height:115%; font-size:11pt; letter-spacing:-0.2pt"> </span><span style="line-height:115%; font-size:11pt">inadequado ou indisciplina do ALUNO; 2) condutas desrespeitosas do próprio CONTRATANTE; 3) no caso de inadimplência de três mensalidades consecutivas.</span>
